      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "$24,500 - Ready for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and is perfect for someone looking for dependable transportation with plenty of life left! While it shows some honest cosmetic wear and signs of its journey, it remains a sturdy and functional choice for your everyday needs.",
