    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows some age with minor scratches, a small dent on the rear bumper, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, but all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It has been regularly serviced, and I have the maintenance records available for your review.",
      "price": 18500.0,
